Detailed Description

Structure to hold the MSS Boot error status data strucutre when booted over SPI for event RL_DEV_AE_MSS_BOOTERRSTATUS_SB.

Note
: The functional APIs shall be sent to radar device only after receiving RL_DEV_AE_MSS_BOOTERRSTATUS_SB Async-event after boot over SPI (Flash is not connected).
